addUpdateTradingPair(address,address).notice: add (or update the RateCalc of existing) trading pair

bRSLC(address).notice: base ETH rewards since last claim

closeStaking(address).notice: prevent new deposits into the pool. Effectivly end that pool.

delegate(address).notice: delegates your voting power to a specific address(sha)

enableRewards(bool).notice: enable or disable BIOP rewards, only for the main ETH pool

sRTG().notice: Send rewards from the proxy to gov and collect a fee

sendTreasuryERC20Funds(address,uint256,a.notice: distribute treasury ERC20 funds to some destination

sendTreasuryFunds(uint256,address).notice: distribute treasury ETH funds to some destination

stake(uint256).notice: stake your BIOP and begin earning rewards

uMNOT(uint256,address).notice: update the maximum time an option can be created for

uMXOT(uint256,address).notice: update the maximum time an option can be created for

undelegate().notice: undelegate your voting power. you will still earn staking rewards  but your voting power won't back any delegate.

updateAccessTiers(address).notice: change the access tiers contract address used to guard all access tier functions

updateBIOPToken(address).notice: update the biop token used by the DAO

updateBetFee(uint256,address).notice: update the fee paid by betters when they make a bet

updateGovProxyFee(uint256).notice: update the fee paid to the user whose tx transfers bet fees from GovProxy to the DelegatedGov

updatePoolLockTime(uint256,address).notice: update soft lock time for the main pool.

updateTrsyAddy(address).notice: change the address that the proxy sends treasury funds too

updateTrsyPercent(uint256).notice: change the amount (as percent) that is sent from proxy to treasury

withdraw(uint256).notice: withdraw your BIOP and stop earning rewards. You must undelegate before you can withdraw
